Malice looked down at the bot that walked in.  he shifted Elita to the crook of one arm and picked up Camoflage with the other.  He held her in the crook of that arm so she could see everyone.
&quot;Elita, Camoflage, this is my half sister Organics.  She came all the way here to see little ol&#39; me.&quot;
Organics grinned.  He somehow remained the same after three centuries.  Not just in personality, but his, and her own face looked almost exactly the way it did three hundred years later.  She pushed all the rumors about his temper and ruthlessness aside, they couldn&#39;t possibly be true.

Could they?
&quot;Hello little ones.  As Neutronics said, I&#39;m Organics.&quot;
She stepped a litle closer and inspected the children Malice was carrying.
&quot;Oh, they&#39;re so cute!  Are they yours?&quot; she asked as innocently as she could.
Malice stars at his sister with a blank stare for a moment.  
&quot;WHAT?  OF COURSE NOT!  I just happen to be baby sitting, that&#39;s all!&quot;
Malice had been in an incredibly good mood as of late, but his sister knew which button to push.  But she also knew how to make it up to him, too.
&quot;Oh don&#39;t be so grouchy.  Here, I&#39;ll take care of these two so you and your new lady friend can do what ever you were before.&quot; she said, holding out here ams.
Malice looked at the children in is arms.
&quot;Well, what do you two want?  Stay with me or go and play with her?&quot;


